1040
01:19:58,793 --> 01:20:01,130
Feliç aniversari.

1041
01:20:02,489 --> 01:20:05,482
Com ho celebrarem les 3 aquesta nit.

1042
01:20:05,483 --> 01:20:08,529
-Amb molt malbaratament.

1043
01:20:09,938 --> 01:20:13,010
